data.description: Located in the heart of Mebane this all brick charmer boasts 4 Bedrooms & 2 full Baths. You will enjoy all your formals, large spacious kitchen w/large island, tons of counter space & a bay window. Flex room on the 1st floor which would be great for an office. Beautiful soaker tub in 1st floor bath. New Roof in 2019. Get cozy in front of one of the 2 wood burning fireplaces. **HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED** So much more, you just need to come and see!
